          <div class="j-fontContent ls-article-info minh500" tabindex="0">
           <p class="p contentText" id="aria4tpg6r47hv0" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            <span id="aria4ikwbx3xyy4" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             为增强政府规范性文件制定的透明度，充分听取公众的意见和建议，扩大公众参与度，切实提高规范性文件质量和水平，现将《萧县政府投资项目管理办法（征求意见稿）》全文向社会公布，公开征求公众意见，期望广大网友和有关单位积极发表修改意见和建议。现将有关事宜公告如下：
            </span>
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="ariakwrurs306x8" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            <span id="aria2qhan7f5uss" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             一、征询意见的起止时间：
            </span>
            2023年11月30
            <span id="aria9pygx8bwjl8" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             日至2023年12
            </span>
            月29
            <span id="ariadyve8qn6pm0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             日
            </span>
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="aria19lsf9ggca3" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            <span id="aria6w8sgqsllws" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             二、提出意见的方式：
            </span>
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="aria19lsf9ggca3" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            <span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;'>
             1.通过宿州市萧县人民政府网站“调查征集”相应主题页面中留言。
            </span>
            <br/>
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="ariab4dcwrdf67c" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            2.通过信函方式将意见寄至：萧县人民政府A栋1321室，并请在信封上注明“萧县政府投资项目管理办法反馈意见”。
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="arialk7hsop85dc" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            3.通过电子邮件方式将修改意见和建议发送至： xxzwgk@163.com，请在邮件上注明“萧县政府投资项目管理办法反馈意见”。
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="arialk7hsop85dc" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            三、联系方式
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="arialk7hsop85dc" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;' tabindex="0">
            联系单位：萧县发展和改革委员会固定资产投资股  联系电话：
            <span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;'>
             0557-5022817
            </span>
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="ariai3gcr1exk4o" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>
           </p>
           <p align="right" class="p contentText" id="aria3anyk7dqbl8" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto 0.5em 0pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; text-align: right;' tabindex="0">
            <span id="ariag0tgv40qdd4" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             萧县人民政府政务公开办
            </span>
           </p>
           <p align="right" class="p contentText" id="aria2cauwc6uzor" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto 0.5em 0pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; text-align: right;' tabindex="0">
            2023年11月30日
           </p>
           <p class="p contentText" id="aria2cauwc6uzor" setedaria="true" style='margin: 0.5em auto 0.5em 0pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", 宋体, tahoma, Verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; text-align: left;' tabindex="0">
            <br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;"/>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 22pt; font-family: 宋体;">
              萧县政府投资项目管理办法
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 22pt; font-family: 宋体;">
              （征求意见稿）
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; line-height: 28pt;">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
            </span>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第一章总则
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第一条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             为加强政府投资项目管理，建立健全科学的政府投资项目决策程序和组织实施程序，保证工程质量，提高政府投资效益，根据国务院《政府投资条例》以及国家有关政府投资政策、安徽省政府投资管理办法的通知（皖政秘〔
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              2022
             </span>
             〕
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              194
             </span>
             号）等文件规定，结合我县实际，制定本办法。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             本办法所称政府投资，是指在萧县行政区域内使用上级和县本级预算安排的资金进行
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 方正仿宋简体;">
             县本级
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             固定资产投资建设活动，包括新建、扩建、改建、技术改造等。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资资金应当投向市场不能有效配置资源的社会公益服务、公共基础设施、农业农村、生态环境保护、重大科技进步、社会管理、国家安全等公共领域的项目，以非经营性项目为主。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             发挥政府投资资金引导和带动作用，鼓励社会资金投向前款规定的领域。政府应当建立政府投资范围定期评估调整机制，不断优化投资方向和结构。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第四条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资应当遵循科学决策、规范管理、注重绩效、公开透明的原则。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第五条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资应当与经济社会发展水平和财政收支状况相适应。加强项目投资论证，按要求组织开展财政承受能力和债务风险评估。政府及其有关部门不得违法违规举借债务筹措政府投资资金。政府加强对政府投资资金的预算约束。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第六条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资资金按项目安排，以直接投资方式为主；对确需支持的经营性项目，主要采取资本金注入方式，也可以适当采取投资补助、贷款贴息等方式。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             安排政府投资资金，应当平等对待各类投资主体，不得设置歧视性条件。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第七条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             通过建立
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              “
             </span>
             项目库
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ”
             </span>
             等方式，加强对使用政府投资资金项目的储备。县人民政府及以上人民政府批准实施的发展规划、专项规划、区域规划及产业政策等明确的项目，是纳入
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              “
             </span>
             项目库
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ”
             </span>
             的重要依据。
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              “
             </span>
             项目库
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ”
             </span>
             实行动态管理、滚动发展，对于建设依据、建设条件发生重大变化或前期工作长时间未取得实质性进展的项目，可以将其移出
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              “
             </span>
             项目库
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ”
             </span>
             。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第八条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资主管部门和其他有关部门依照本办法和政府规定职责分工，履行相应的政府投资管理职责。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
            </span>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二章政府投资决策
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第九条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府应当根据国民经济和社会发展规划、中期财政规划和国家宏观调控政策，结合财政收支状况，规范使用各类政府投资资金，统筹安排使用政府投资资金项目。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府采取直接投资方式、资本金注入方式投资的项目
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             以下统称
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              “
             </span>
             政府投资项目
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ”),
             </span>
             项目单位应当编制项目建议书、可行性研究报告、初步设计，按照政府投资管理权限和规定的程序，报政府投资主管部门或者政府赋予项目审批权的其他部门
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             以下统称
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              “
             </span>
             项目审批部门
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ”)
             </span>
             审批。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目单位应当严格落实厉行节约要求，加强政府投资项目的前期工作，保证前期工作的深度达到规定要求，并对项目建议书、可行性研究报告、初步设计以及依法应当附具的其他文件的真实性负责，不得弄虚作假。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十一条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目审批，原则上与财政事权和支出责任相匹配，主要由项目所属的同级项目审批部门审批。项目建议书、可行性研究报告一般由投资主管部门审批，初步设计按照国家及省有关规定由项目审批部门审批。跨地区的项目，由所涉及地区共同审批，或者报请共同的上级审批。国家及省另有规定的，从其规定。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             对经济社会发展、社会公众利益有重大影响或者投资规模较大的政府投资项目，投资主管部门在批复项目建议书或可行性研究报告前，应当征求司法行政、自然资源、生态环境、水利
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             水务
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             等部门意见，并核报政府审查同意。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             党政机关办公用房和技术业务用房建设项目审批权限和程序，按照国家及省有关规定执行。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十二条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             除涉及国家秘密的项目外，项目审批部门应当通过投资项目在线审批监管平台
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             以下简称
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              “
             </span>
             在线平台
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ”),
             </span>
             使用在线平台生成的项目代码办理政府投资项目审批手续。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目审批部门应当通过在线平台列明与政府投资有关的规划、产业政策等，公开政府投资项目审批的办理流程、办理时限等，并为项目单位提供相关咨询服务。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十三条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目建议书要对项目建设的必要性、主要建设内容、拟建地点、拟建规模、投资匡算、资金筹措以及社会效益和经济效益、绩效评估等进行初步分析，并附相关文件资料。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十四条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             投资主管部门对符合发展规划、区域规划、专业规划及产业政策，已落实资金筹措等建设条件，且确有必要建设的项目，批准项目建议书。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十五条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目单位依据项目建议书批复文件，组织开展可行性研究，自行编制或委托具有相应能力的工程咨询单位编制项目可行性研究报告，对项目技术和经济上的可行性、投资估算以及社会效益、节能、节水、资源综合利用、生态环境影响、社会稳定风险等进行全面分析论证，并落实主要建设条件。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             在可行性研究阶段，应当完成法律、行政法规明确的项目审批前置手续，按照有关规定获得相关部门审查意见。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十六条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目可行性研究报告应当包含项目的勘察、设计、施工、监理以及重要设备、材料等采购活动的具体招标范围、招标组织形式和招标方式等内容。国家及省另有规定的，从其规定。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十七条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             对于采取资本金注入方式的政府投资项目，应在可行性研究报告中明确项目资本金比例及筹措方式等内容。对于采取政府和社会资本合作机制实施的项目，应当符合国家及省相关规定，不得新增政府隐性债务。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十八条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             投资主管部门对符合规划选址、社会效益、节能、节水、资源综合利用、生态环境影响、社会稳定风险等要求，且在技术和经济上可行，具备建设条件的项目，批准可行性研究报告。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第十九条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目单位应委托具有相应资质的设计单位进行初步设计。初步设计应当符合国家及省有关规定和可行性研究报告批复文件的有关要求，明确各个单项工程
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             单位工程
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             的建设内容、建设规模、建设标准、用地规模、主要材料、设备规格和技术参数等设计方案，并据此编制投资概算，不得超标准、超规模设计。投资概算应当包括国家及省规定的项目建设所需的全部费用。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目审批部门对符合可行性研究报告以及国家有关标准和规范要求的初步设计及投资概算，予以批准
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             核定
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十一条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             经批准
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             核定
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             的初步设计及投资概算是项目建设实施和控制政府投资项目总投资的依据。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             初步设计提出的投资概算超过经批准的可行性研究报告提出投资估算
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              10%
             </span>
             的，项目单位应当向项目审批部门报告。对初步设计未按可行性研究报告批复要求、擅自扩大工程量或提高建设标准的，项目审批部门应当不予批准其概算，并要求项目单位重新按照可行性研究报告批复进行初步设计、提出合理概算。对可行性研究不充分、不深入，导致估算不能满足建设需要的，项目审批部门应当要求项目单位重新编制和报送可行性研究报告。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十二条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目建议书、可行性研究报告、初步设计批复文件中应当规定文件的有效期，有效期一般不超过
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              2
             </span>
             年。国家及省另有规定的，从其规定。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目审批部门应当通过在线平台与有关部门共享批复文件。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十三条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             对经济社会发展、社会公众利益有重大影响或者投资规模较大的政府投资项目，项目审批部门应当在中介服务机构评估、公众参与、专家评议、风险评估的基础上作出是否批准的决定。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             中介服务机构与编制项目建议书、可行性研究报告、初步设 计的中介服务机构为同一单位、存在控股、管理关系或者负责人为同一人的，该中介服务机构不得承担该项目的评估工作。中介服务机构与项目单位存在控股、管理关系或者负责人为同一人的，该中介服务机构不得承担该项目评估工作。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             中介服务机构评估、专家评议费用由项目审批部门承担，中介服务机构或有关人员不得收取项目单位的任何费用。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十四条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             对政府投资项目不予批准的，应当书面通知项目单位并说明理由。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十五条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             对下列政府投资项目，可以按照国家及省有关规定简化需要报批的文件和审批程序：
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             一
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             经国务院及有关部门或者省级人民政府批准的发展规划、专项规划、区域规划中已经明确的项目，可以不再编制、审批项目建议书，直接编制、审批可行性研究报告
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             代项目建议书
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             二
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             总投资在
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              3000
             </span>
             万元以下的项目
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             含改扩建项目
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              ),
             </span>
             可 以合并编制、审批项目建议书、可行性研究报告。其中，总投资在
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              1000
              <span>
              </span>
             </span>
             万元以下项目
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             含改扩建项目
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             且建设内容单一、技术方案简单的，可以直接编制、审批初步设计。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             三
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             为应对自然灾害、事故灾难、公共卫生事件、社会安全事件等突发事件需要紧急建设的项目，可以合并编制、审批项目建议书、可行性研究报告和初步设计。县级以上人民政府决定先行下达投资计划的，应及时补办项目相关审批手续。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             前款第二项规定属于地方审批权限且建设内容单一、技术方案简单的项目具体范围，依据省级投资主管部门作出的具体规定。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             国家对简化政府投资项目审批另有规定的，依照规定执行。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十六条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             直接编制初步设计的政府投资项目，一般由投资行业主管部门审批。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             按规定简化报批手续的项目取得项目代码后，可由行业主管部门出具前期工作意见函。项目单位可凭前期工作意见函向自然资源
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             规划
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             等部门申请办理建设项目用地预审与选址意见书等审批手续。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十七条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             合并编制、审批项目建议书、可行性研究报告的，可行性研究报告应当增加项目必要性论证内容；直接编制、审批初步设计的，应当完成法律、行政法规明确的项目审批前置手续，报批文件应当达到初步设计要求，并增加项目必要性和可行性论证内容。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十八条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             采取投资补助、贷款贴息等方式安排政府投资资金的，项目单位应当按照国家及省有关规定办理手续。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三章政府投资年度计划
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第二十九条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             行业主管部门对其负责编制本行业、本领域的政府投资年度计划。
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312; color: windowtext;">
             单个项目投资额在
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              3000
             </span>
             万元以上（包含
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              3000
             </span>
             万元），需由项目单位提请县政府有关会议研究决定。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             列入政府投资年度计划的项目应当符合下列条件：
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             一
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             采取直接投资、资本金注入方式的，可行性研究报告已经批准或者投资概算已经核定。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             二
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             采取投资补助、贷款贴息等方式的，已经按照国家有关规定办理手续。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             三
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             政府有关部门规定的其他条件。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十一条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             申请政府投资年度计划的项目，项目单位应当编制年度资金申请报告。年度资金申请报告应包含以下主要内容：
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             一
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             项目单位的基本情况。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             二
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             项目的基本情况，包括项目名称、项目代码、建设内容、总投资及资金来源、建设条件落实情况以及完成审批
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             核准、备案
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             情况等。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             三
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             申请投资的主要理由和政策依据，以及申请金额。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             四
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             项目绩效情况分析。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             五
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             其他需要说明的情况。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目单位应对所提交的年度资金申请报告内容及附件的真实性负责。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             续建项目可简化资金申请报告内容，主要说明上一年度项目绩效完成情况、本年度拟申请的资金和项目绩效情况分析。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十二条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资年度计划下达后，必须严格执行，任何单位和个人不得擅自变更。确需调整的，由项目单位或行业主管部门提出申请并重新履行审批手续。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十三条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资年度计划编制应当加强绩效管理。绩 效目标作为申请和安排政府投资的重要依据，应与政府投资计划同步申报、同步下达。投资主管部门和其他有关部门应当每年对政府投资计划绩效目标实现情况组织评价，加强绩效评价结果运用。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十四条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             财政部门应当根据经批准的预算，按照法律、行政法规和国库管理的有关规定，及时、足额办理政府投资资金拨付。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第四章政府投资项目实施
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十五条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目开工建设，应当符合有关法律
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 宋体;">
             、
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             法规和本办法规定的建设条件；不符合规定条件的，不得开工建设。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             国务院规定应当审批开工报告的重大政府投资项目，按照规定办理开工报告审批手续后方可开工建设。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十六条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目应当按照项目审批部门批准的 建设地点、建设规模和建设内容实施，不得擅自变更；拟变更建设地点或者拟对建设规模和建设内容等作较大变更的，应当按照规定的程序报原可行性研究报告审批部门重新审批。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十七条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目有下列情形之一的，原则上不予重新审批：
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             一
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             项目已基本建设完成的。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             二
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             项目单位在建设过程中擅自改变建设地点、建设内容和建设规模的。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             三
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             项目实施过程中其他违法违规行为造成重大社会影响的 。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十八条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             对于项目单位缺少相关专业技术人员和建设管理经验的政府直接投资项目实行代理建设制度
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              (
             </span>
             代建制
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             。项目代建实施单位按照与项目单位签订的合同，承担项目建设实施的相关权利义务，严格执行项目投资概算、质量标准和建设工期等要求。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             鼓励政府投资项目推行工程总承包、全过程咨询服务，提倡采用建筑信息模型
             <span>
             </span>
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 宋体;">
             (BIM)
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 宋体;">
             、
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             装配式建筑、绿色建筑等新技术、新工艺。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第三十九条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目所需资金应当按照国家及省有关规定确保落实到位。政府投资项目不得由施工单位垫资建设。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第四十条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目建设投资原则上不得超过经核定的投资概算。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             因国家政策调整、价格上涨、地质条件发生重大变化以及自然灾害等不可抗力因素导致原核定概算不能满足工程实际需要确需增加投资概算的，项目单位应当提出调整方案及资金来源，按照规定的程序报原初步设计审批部门审批或者投资概算核定部门核定；涉及预算调整或调剂的，按照有关法律、法规和国家及省有关规定办理。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第四十一条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目应当按照国家及省有关规定合理确定并严格执行建设工期，任何单位和个人不得非法干预。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第四十二条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目建成后，应当按照国家及省有关规定进行竣工验收，并在竣工验收合格后及时办理竣工财务决算，报同级财政部门审批。对政府投资项目竣工验收合格后形成的固定资产，项目单位应当依法办理产权登记。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             政府投资项目结余的财政资金，应当按照国家及省有关规定缴回国库。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第四十三条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             项目审批部门应当按照国家及省有关规定，选择有代表性的已建成政府投资项目，委托中介服务机构对所选项目进行后评价。后评价应当根据项目建成后的实际效果，对项目审批和实施进行全面评价并提出明确意见，作为规划制定、项目审批、资金安排、项目管理的重要参考依据。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第五章监督管理
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p align="center" setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
             </span>
            </b>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32.15pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <b style="font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 黑体;">
              第四十四条
             </span>
            </b>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             按照谁审批谁监管、谁主管谁监管的原则，项目审批部门以及依法对政府投资项目负有监督管理职责的其他部门，应当采取在线监测、现场核查等方式，加强对政府投资项目实施情况的监督检查。监督检查的主要内容包括：
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             一
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             建设手续是否齐全。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             二
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             建设进度是否符合投资计划要求。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             (
            </span>
            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋, 仿宋_GB2312;">
             三
             <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;">
              )
             </span>
             建设资金是否到位，资金使用是否规范。
            </span>
           </p>
           <p setedaria="true" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt;" tabindex="0">
